  kato: {
    description:
      "BY STRONG WOMEN, FOR STRONG WOMEN\nKato is an Egyptian local brand inspired by the artistry of the Nubian homes in Aswan. Halla, the founder, launched the brand in Cairo in summer of 2019, during her first year of university, bringing together her love for fashion and design with a mission to empower underprivileged women. Kato’s team is constantly exploring new materials and techniques with an aim to revive and reinterpret traditional crafts such as hand beading, crocheting, and fabric manipulation. Kato is proud to be working with more than 50 women who come from underprivileged areas all around Egypt to hand craft the bags with tons of love and passion.",
    logo: "/logos/kato.avif",
  },
  kika: {
    description:
      "The team behind KIKA has long been immersed in sunny climates, finding solace in the beach as their constant escape from city life. This lifestyle instilled in them a deep appreciation for various products.\n\nRecognizing a need for luxury, sustainable, and fresh garments in the Arab world at an affordable price range, KIKA was founded. Their vision is to provide the Arab world with exceptional curated pieces while also expanding their offerings to include a wide range of high-quality fashion items. At KIKA, they take pride in manufacturing these products in their own factory, ensuring the utmost attention to detail and maintaining full control over the production process.\n\nThey are committed to curating clean, good-quality garments that introduce new designs regularly. Their aim is to offer customers a diverse and ever-evolving range of products that exemplify luxury, sustainability, and style. With a focus on superior craftsmanship and ethical manufacturing practices, KIKA strives to create a unique shopping experience for customers.\n\nExplore their website and discover an array of carefully crafted products that embody their passion for fashion and style. Join them as they embark on this journey, where KIKA becomes the destination for all things fashion. Welcome to KIKA, where they bring the latest trends and timeless elegance to the Arab world.\n\nOUR CORE VALUES\nHIGH QUALITY PRODUCTS\n\nManufactured in Egypt, KIKA understands the importance of long-lasting and sustainable fabrics that are comfortable and durable, making the quality of their products one of the most important aspects.\n\nSOCIALLY DRIVEN\n\nWhen thinking of fashion, sun, music, and fun come to mind, which is why KIKA chooses to include a social aspect within the brand. Whether that be through launch parties or photoshoots with friends, they like to keep it light, fresh, and fun.\n\nCREATIVITY\n\nThere is no lack of fashion brands out there, which is why KIKA places an emphasis on the creativity of their lines, colors, patterns, and editorials. By including a mix of their own style as well as what is trending, they aim to be as creative as possible.\n\nCUSTOMER SERVICE\n\nKIKA constantly aims to create great customer interactions by practicing respect, authenticity, and accountability.",
    logo: "/logos/kika.webp",
  },
  kncpt: {
    description:
      "\nWelcome to KNCPT, where innovation meets style, and the concept transcends mere collections—it's a bridge between generations. Rooted in the belief that fashion should surpass generational boundaries, KNCPT specializes in curating a unique blend of pieces that seamlessly connect Gen Z and millennials.\n\nDive into KNCPT's curated collections, where fashion serves as a language that speaks to diverse tastes. From vibrant and energetic ensembles to sophisticated, timeless pieces, the range caters to every individual preference, fostering an inclusive space for style exploration.\n\nEmbark on the Fashion Revolution\nExperience a fashion revolution that challenges traditional boundaries. Explore KNCPT's collections, connect with fellow fashion enthusiasts, and become part of a movement that transcends fleeting trends. KNCPT extends beyond garments; it's a celebration of connections, diverse styles, and the inclusive fashion community being crafted. Step into a fashion house where everyone is not just welcomed but celebrated, and where every style discovers its rightful place.",
    logo: "/logos/kncpt.avif",
  },
  konga: {
    description:
      "Step into the rebellious world of the Konga Collective, an Egyptian streetwear brand established in 2020 that transcends fashion to become a fearless movement embodying the duality inherent in Gen Z's pursuit of contradicting interests. Renowned for mastering the art of denim, Konga captures the essence of individuality and resilience in every stitch, reflecting the clash of opposing forces that define our generation. Beyond clothing, Konga is a community, a tribe united by a commitment to rewriting the rules and celebrating the chaos of pursuing dreams that seem worlds apart. Join the collective, where rebellion is refined, and the streets of Egypt become a runway for the unapologetically authentic.",
    logo: "/logos/konga.svg",
  },
